:::Godfather/Cyclonus/Scourge:::

::Godfather reaches the Decepticon base(with Shockaract i hope?) and opens 
his comm::
Godfather: Yo dudes! This is Godfather. Me and my commander are here to join 
you.
::Cyclonus and Scourge open the door. Scourge looks to Cyclonus::
Scourge: Whatchya think?
Cyclonus: They look pretty tough.
::he looks to Godfather and Shockaract(if hes there)::
Cyclonus: i'll check with Megatron if you can join.
::He opens his comm to Megatron::
Cyclonus: hey Megatron, Two tough looking bots are here and they want to join 
us. Should i let them in?
